706203f-b.text:
Park Avenue, east from NAVY =========== Street (something) showing demolition of buildings for the Fort Greene Houses. The area already cleared is the block from St. Edwards Street to North Elliott Place.
Late summer, 1939
Views 1,2
P.L. Sperr

Note: View 3 shows the view(?) east from Navy Street and the Wallabout (?) Houses nearing completion. Views 1,2 are east from St. Edwards Street.
